!!!WORK IN PROGRESS!!!

The xcorrSound tool compares soundwaves using cross correlation and finds the best overlap.

INSTALL

    Kør

    ./createtarball.sh

    Nu kan tjærebolden (xcorrSound.tar) distribueres.

Beskrivelse af hvordan man bygger og installerer programmet på en given maskine.

    Export XcorrSound

    svn export https://merkur.statsbiblioteket.dk/svn/scape-xcorrsound/tags/xcorrSound_v1.01

    Go to the 'xcorrSound/fftw-3-2-2' folder.

    Run the following

    ./configure --prefix=<fftw>
    make
    make install

where <fftw> is the subfolder fftw where xcorrSound_v1.01 was checked out. fx /home/larm/jsn/xcorrSound_v1.01/fftw

    go to the 'xcorrSound' folder.

    Run

    make xcorrSound

    Test that it works: (should print out how to use this tool)

    ./xcorrSound

USE

Syntax:

xcorrSound <<EOF
ANALYSIS_FILE_1.wav
ANALYSIS_FILE_2.wav
EOF

